><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.filmstudycenter.org/robert_gardner.html\">Robert Gardner Profile</a> at  The Film Study Center at <a href=\"/wiki/Harvard_University\" title=\"Harvard University\">Harvard University</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://astro.temple.edu/~ruby/ruby/gardner.html\">An Anthropological Critique Of The Films Of Robert Gardner</a> at <a href=\"/wiki/Temple_University\" title=\"Temple University\">Temple University</a></li>\n<li>Ruby, Jay. <i>Picturing Culture: Explorations of Film and Anthropology.</i> Chicago: U. of Chicago Press, 2000.</li>\n<li>Heider, Karl. <i>Ethnographic Film.</i> Austin: University of Texas Press, 1978.</li>\n<li>Schmitz M. Norbert, Gupta, Susanne. \"Robert Gardners \"Forest of Bliss\" - Dokumentarfilm als visuelle Poesie, UVK Konstanz, 2012. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-3-86764-409-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-3-86764-409-9\">978-3-86764-409-9</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Robert_Gardner_(anthropologist)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robertgardner.net/\">Robert Gardner website</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fas.harvard.edu/~fsc/robert-gardner.html\">Robert Gardner</a> at <a href=\"/wiki/Harvard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Harvard\">Harvard</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://independencia.fr/EPHEMERE/RENCONTRE_ROB